ComicInfo.Summary:
Cherry Hammer recruits Parker Girl Kelly and her unique killer instincts to help catch the killer of Piper May and all roads lead to her husband, billionaire Zackary May. Meanwhile Katchoo succeeds in luring May’s defense team on a chase that leads them back to California and the scene of the crime. Don’t miss a single issue of this action-packed limited series!
